snippet.title: Quake - Rapture (Part 1 of 4)
snippet.description:
Like the video of me doing Guncotton @ Nightmare, here I heroicly storm the castle of Rapture. There is a good amount of gibbing in this one.

Rapture is a Quake episode by Tronyn and [Kona], released in September 2001. Be sure to check out [Kona]'s site at ethereal-hell.telefragged.com and visit Tronyn's Bazaar at tronyn.planetquake.gamespy.com.
